io.spine.server.entity

Class AbstractVersionableEntity<I,S extends com.google.protobuf.Message>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.server.entity.AbstractEntity<I,S>
      • io.spine.server.entity.AbstractVersionableEntity<I,S>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - the type of the entity ID
    S - the type of the entity state
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Entity<I,S>, EntityWithLifecycle<I,S>, VersionableEntity<I,S>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TransactionalEntity

    public abstract class AbstractVersionableEntity<I,S extends com.google.protobuf.Message>
extends AbstractEntity<I,S>
implements VersionableEntity<I,S>, EntityWithLifecycle<I,S>
    An abstract base for entities with versions.

    The entity keeps only its latest state and version information associated with this state.
